<div align='center'><font size='4'><b>BACKYARD BASH!</b></font><br>
<img src='http://graphics.millsberry.com/site_gfx/interiors/gazette/news_grill_2007-06-07.jpg' border='1'>
</div>
<br>
<b>Thursday, June  7, 2007</b> &mdash; Millsberry citizens are very creative when it comes to decorating their houses. By touring a random sample of homes, you&#039;ll see some really innovative design ideas. Ever thought of making stairs out of mounted single wall shelves? How about using an anvil as a coffee table?  <br><br>With the arrival of summer, citizens are turning their attention to their yards. After all, what better way to kick off summer than with a big party in your backyard? When it comes to yards, citizens use the space in many different ways. Pools, flowerbeds, and lounge chairs come into play.<br>
<br>
Now that it&#039;s nice out, how about installing that pool you&#039;ve been dreaming about? Or why not set up a little corner with planters and stepping stones? Spend some time making your yard <i>the</i> place to hang out. Set out some chairs so you and your friends can hang out in the sun every day this summer.<br><br>Looking for ideas? There are some amazing new items going on sale today. Ever wanted a treehouse or tiki torches? Head to <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=8">Peterson&#039;s Construction and Hardware Emporium</a> and pick up this must-have stuff. You may need to build a whole new yard to hold everything! <br><br>Enjoy decorating, and be sure to visit other people&#039;s homes to see what they&#039;ve done with their outdoor space. Open your home up to visitors so more people can see how creative you are. It&#039;s summer&mdash;put on your sunscreen and get outside and play! Spruce up your yard space, and invite your friends over for a cool BBQ!</div>


<br><hr><br>

<div id='gazette_story'>
<div align='center'><font size='3'><b>PLAY OUTDOORS</b></font><br>
</div>
<br>
It&#039;s June! The weather&#039;s magnificent. Why don&#039;t you head to <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park/">Peabody Park</a> and play? There are plenty of ways to have fun outside (and get some exercise too). Hit some long balls at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=160">Sherman Home Run Derby</a>. Score a <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=484">Tricky Touchdown</a> like a pro. Show off your killer moves in the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=60">Peabody Park Half-Pipe Competition</a>. Or bike to the Community Center pool for some head-to-head <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=440">Bumper Boats</a> action. <br><br>Have fun, and flex those athletic muscles outside!</div>
